title: How to Not Have a Shitty Day

description:
Life is up and down. That's why in this episode, I am going to teach you how to save a bad day and make it amazing!

 

Want to master your mindset? Every Monday I send out an email with mindset tips for the week, click here to receive that email: http://mondayemail.com/
